@node "main.registration" "Registration"
@prev "main.config"
@next "main.thanx"

    To register MicroBBS, simply send me 30.- DM, fill out and send me (either
    per email or snailmail) the following form and I will send you a keyfile
    back. For either snail- or crashmail add 5.- for "shipping".


    Name:       ........................................
    Street:     ........................................
    Country:    ........................................
    State:      ........................................

    Voice:      ........................................
    Data:       ........................................

    EMail:      ........................................

    Send as     Crash []    Snail []     EMail []

@endnode
